[src:grain-language/pattern-matching] The wildcard pattern (often written as `_`) is also simple: like a variable name, it matches any value, but does not bind the value to any name.
[src:grain-language/pattern-matching] Algorithms for matching wildcards in simple string-matching situations have been developed in a number of recursive and non-recursive varieties.
